  <brief_title>Observational Study in Preterm Infants With Intracranial Hemorrhage</brief_title>
  <official_title>Observational Study in Preterm Infants With and Without Intracranial Hemorrhage: Longitudinal Assessment of Cerebral Oxygenation, Perfusion and Function</official_title>
